# Instagram Fliers

- Default: 1080×1080 post. Also support 1080×1350 portrait and 1080×1920 story.
- Keep text inside the safe inset from `tokens.spacing.safe`.
- Stories need extra top/bottom clearance for Instagram UI chrome.
- Brand/logo near the top; CTA near the bottom.
- Full-bleed background imagery; overlay gradient only for text legibility.
- Component + colocated CSS in `src/fliers/instagram/`.
- Studio wires size via `width` / `height` props — do not hardcode size only in CSS.
